high_descs: walk over to the kitchen sink
grab a clear cup out of the kitchen sink
walk on over to the fridge
place the cup inside the fridge, let it cool and then take it out again
bring the cup over to the kitchen sink again
place the cup in the cabinet below the kitchen sink on the right
anns.task_desc: put a cooled cup underneath the kitchen sink

high_descs: Pick up the glass from the sink.
Bring the glass to the fridge.
Chill the glass in the fridge.
Bring the glass to the sink.
Put the glass in the right cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled glass in the right cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the table then turn right to the sink.
Pick up the glass in the sink.
Turn around then head left to the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the glass inside to chill for 5 seconds then remove it.
Close the fridge and head back to the sink.
Place the glass inside of the cabinet below the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the chilled glass in the cabinet below the sink.
